{
  "stem": "27335.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But under one condition-- we go in a meeting in [INAUDIBLE] where nobody else see us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they-- gave up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did they want from you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they cursed me, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who are-- you are-- you are a vagabond.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are this and that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You claim-- you claim you served-- you were the boyfriend and who knows what to Hannah Szenes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hannah Szenes was a Zionist hero, and so on and so forth, some [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's-- [INAUDIBLE] Jewish Defense League here is an extreme Zionist gang.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes I met them at the-- at the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is not here, but someday I will go [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not exactly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was on probation, even by my party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and my staff, really-- editor board and the leadership of the Hungarian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From-- I arrived back in in the beginning of June 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got two weeks or three weeks furlough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Went out west to see my family and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when I came back, nothing said-- absolutely nothing-- not even Tim Buck, you see, who was responsible, who were recruiting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE], because after all, we were with the British intelligence, you see-- in cahoot with the British intelligence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were in contact with that goes back centuries, at least 300 centuries, the [INAUDIBLE] and they knew what kind of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were-- we were rubbing shoulders with hem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then Tim Buck went back to-- went back to Hungary three times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I was checked out in Budapest, in [NON-ENGLISH], in Prague, in Moscow, because I was in contact with the-- with the [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Malinowski ?] and [INAUDIBLE] through-- through what you call runners and furnished them with information inside-- inside, and encircle city, and with very great success.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
